cdata.name: Capdax
cdata.desc: Capdax is a cryptocurrency exchange for beginner and professional traders alike. It features a simple interface allows for an easy to understand introduction, while experienced traders will find a full suite of powerful tools and lightning fast trade execution speeds. Featured copy-trading allows traders to seamlessly follow the portfolios of others. The XCD token is an ERC20 token used within the Capdax platform.
